ose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>本对象代表了一个关于&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Functions/eval\" title=\"en/Core_JavaScript_1.5_Reference/Global_Functions/eval\">eval</a> 函数的错误。此异常不再会被 JavaScript 抛出，但是 EvalError 对象仍然保持兼容性。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code>new EvalError([<var>message</var>[, <var>fileName</var>[, <var>lineNumber</var>]]])</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"message\">message</dt>\n <dd>可选参数：可阅读的关于错误的描述。</dd>\n <dt id=\"filename_非标准\">fileName (非标准)</dt>\n <dd>可选参数：代码中导致异常的文件的文件名。</dd>\n <dt id=\"linenumber_非标准\">lineNumber (非标准)</dt>\n <dd>可选参数：代码中导致异常的代码的行号。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"prototype\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/EvalError\" title=\"en/Core_JavaScript_1.5_Reference/Global_Objects/EvalError/prototype\">prototype</a></dt>\n <dd>允许向 EvalError 对象中添加自定义属性。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"methods","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<p>全局的 EvalError 对象本身不包含任何方法，然而它通过原型链继承了一些方法。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"evalerror_实例","title":"<code>EvalError</code> 实例","isH3":false,"content":"","titleAsText":"EvalError 实例"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":true,"content":"<p>{{page('/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/EvalError/prototype', 'Properties')}}</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":true,"content":"<p>{{page('/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/EvalError/prototype', 'Methods')}}</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例子","title":"例子","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>EvalError</code> 不在当前 ECMAScript 规范中使用，因此不会被运行时抛出。但是对象本身仍然与规范的早期版本向后兼容。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"创建_evalerror","title":"创建&nbsp;<code>EvalError</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\"><code>try {\n  throw new EvalError('Hello', 'someFile.js', 10);\n} catch (e) {\n  console.log(e instanceof EvalError); // true\n  console.log(e.message);              // \"Hello\"\n  console.log(e.name);                 // \"EvalError\"\n  console.log(e.fileName);             // \"someFile.js\"\n  console.log(e.lineNumber);           // 10\n  console.log(e.columnNumber);         // 0\n  console.log(e.stack);                // \"@Scratchpad/2:2:9\\n\"\n}</code></pre>","titleAsText":"创建 EvalError"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">规范</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状态</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">注释</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/publications/files/ECMA-ST-ARCH/ECMA-262,%203rd%20edition,%20December%201999.pdf\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"ECMAScript 3rd Edition (ECMA-262)\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 3rd Edition (ECMA-262)</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>初始定义。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/5.1/#sec-15.11.6.1\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 5.1 (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">EvalError</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>本规范中未使用。为了保持向后兼容。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-native-error-types-used-in-this-standard-evalerror\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">EvalError</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>本规范中未使用。为了保持向后兼容。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-native-error-types-used-in-this-standard-evalerror\" 